N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 690.4 - Volunteer program

State Regulations

The members of the committees on
character and fitness, as volunteers, are expressly authorized to participate
in a State-sponsored volunteer program within the meaning of subdivision 1 of
section
17
of the
